name: VR Schoool - Solar System
summary:
🚀 Travel across the Solar System and learn about planets in a calm, immersive VR experience for curious minds.
🌌 Fly among the planets, orbit the Sun, and discover fascinating facts about our cosmic neighborhood like never before. See the planets in stunning 3D detail, understand their unique features, and explore moons, rings, and asteroids up close.
📚 Part of the VR Schoool Series — bringing science, space, and exploration to life through Virtual Reality.
